<title><![CDATA[Black beluga lentil soup]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[Black beluga lentils are similar to Puy lentils but they are grown in the cool climate of America's Northern plains. Some lentils tend to go murky when cooked but these beauties keep their remarkable satin-black colour.]]></description>
