<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">
        <step><![CDATA[Gently cook the onion, ginger, garlic, chilli and spices in the butter for 3-4 minutes, add the vegetable stock and lentils, season, bring to the boil and simmer for 40 minutes or until the lentils are soft. Blend about one-third of the soup in a liquidiser until smooth and return to the pan. Adjust the seasoning if necessary and add the coriander. Serve with half a spoonful of yoghurt on top.]]></step>
      </directions>
